These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, rose, iris
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, yellow, white, lavender
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growsorchid and the person who likes yellow##2
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
3. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growsorchid##7
4. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who likes white##1
6. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Flower   | rose | iris       | daisy | orchid        |
| Color      | white  | yellow | lavender        | chestnut |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, lemonade, coffee
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, daffodil, begonia
1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the person drinking lemonade##7
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage     | lemonade | 7up       | coffee         | tea     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | begonia | daffodil | bellflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bluemaster, cain, vegafina
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, ice-hockey, tennis
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##7
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the bluemaster-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | vegafina | cain | dannemann  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | rowing  | tennis   | skateboarding |

