.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, australian, canadian, colombian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, amaryllis, iris
1. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
2. the british is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the colombian##7
3. the canadian is the person who growsiris##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the australian is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Nationality   | australian | british | colombian       | canadian |
| Flower   | tulip      | zinnia   | amaryllis | iris  |

