.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, designer, doctor, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, salsa, soul, pop
1. the fan pop is on the left or right of the designer##3
2. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the fan salsa##5
3. the pilot is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the fan pop is somewhere between the designer and the pilot##7
5. the fan pop is on the left of the fan soul##1
6. the fan salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
7. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the pilot is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Job         | doctor | pilot   | fisherman | designer |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | salsa | pop      | soul |

