.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, singing, cooking, camping
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, snowmobile, boat
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##7
7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby      | singing | fishing      | cooking | camping     |
| Transport   | car    | boat | motorbike   | snowmobile |

