.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
House: craftsman, colonial, townhouse, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, baseball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
2. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the craftsman house and the townhouse house##7
5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House          | art-deco    | craftsman   | colonial | townhouse  |
| Sport   | tennis | baseball | volleyball    | handball |

