2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
3. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the bike##7
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike | subway | bike |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks   | woodworking    | cooking       | dancing  |

