There 4 different types of food: garlic, broccoli, cherry, mango
1. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the person eating mango##7
2. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person eating cherry##6
3. the person eating broccoli is not the oliveros-smoker##6
4. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
5. the chaman-smoker is the person eating garlic##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | chaman | old-henry | pall-mall | oliveros |
| Food           | garlic    | broccoli   | mango  | cherry      |

