2. the argentine is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the van is between the person driving the train and the indonesian##2
6. the argentine is somewhere between the indonesian and the person driving the train##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Transport   | scooter | van | train | taxi   |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | argentine      | pakistani      | indian |

