2. the software-developer is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the person playing billiard is not the project-manager##6
4. the mechanic is on the left of the person playing domino##1
5. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
6. the firefighter is somewhere between the project-manager and the mechanic##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Job   | mechanic | firefighter | software-developer | project-manager |
| Game   | billiard  | domino    | backgammon    | poker  |

