.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, tea, fanta, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: plum, potato, cauliflower, cherry
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating plum##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating potato##6
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating potato##1
6. the person eating potato is somewhere between the person eating plum and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage       | mirinda | water | tea | fanta |
| Food   | plum   | cherry      | potato        | cauliflower  |

