2. the art-deco house is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the townhouse house##7
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
4. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the townhouse house##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Sport      | handball   | sailing | snowboarding | badminton   |
| House   | tower | townhouse   | art-deco | victorian |

