2. the person traveling to new-york is between the fan metal and the fan r&b##2
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
6. the fan r&b is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| City    | rome   | miami  | new-york  | london |
| Music-Genre   | punk | metal | country | r&b    |

