1. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere between the dutch and the person who growsaconite##7
2. the dutch is on the right of the polish##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the polish is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Flower         | aconite    | daffodil | azalea     | orchid |
| Nationality   | thai | australian  | polish | dutch |

 